headline: CSX President And Chief Executive Officer to Address Morgan Stanley’s 13th Annual Laguna Conference
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Sept. 04, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) President and Chief Executive Officer, Joe Hinrichs, will address Morgan Stanley’s 13th Annual Laguna Conference in California on Thursday, September 11, at 8:30 a.m. Pacific time. This address will be broadcast live via webcast at http://investors.csx.com. A replay will be available following the conclusion of this event.
